374
00:23:33,291 --> 00:23:35,166
You start running...

375
00:23:35,250 --> 00:23:38,208
With the belief that
something good lies ahead.

376
00:23:38,291 --> 00:23:40,333
But don't fool
yourself...

377
00:23:40,416 --> 00:23:43,541
You're about to find
a new kind of despair

378
00:23:43,625 --> 00:23:46,375
"At the End of
